# Neuman Brain

> [!INFO] Summary
> A privacy-first, local-only productivity platform combining notes, tasks, time tracking, calendar, and AI capabilities in a single unified dashboard. All data stays on user's device (IndexedDB-based, 50GB+ capacity). "Your Brain. Your Data. Your Device."

